| **Nevins** | *Study in Power* / *Heroic Age* | Sympathetic scholarly biography |
| **Fosdick** | *Story of the Rockefeller Foundation* | Insider account; Fosdick was JDR Jr.'s adviser |
| **Yergin** | *The Prize* | Oil industry context |
| **Tarbell** | *History of Standard Oil* | The muckraking expose |
| **Bringhurst** | *Antitrust and the Oil Monopoly* | Legal history of dissolution |
| **McGovern & Guttridge** | *The Great Coalfield War* | Definitive Ludlow account |
| **Noll** | *The Aryan Christ* | Jung and Edith McCormick |
| **Hidy & Hidy** | *History of Standard Oil (NJ)* | Corporate history |
| **Collier & Horowitz** | *The Rockefellers* | Critical family biography |

